reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So impressed with how much you can fit with these
reviews.reviewText: Fantastic for staying organized while traveling and compacting your suitcase. The zippers have frayed a bit on some of the cubes but overall well made. Have used them on a week long and month long trip. I will never pack a suitcase without packing cubes again

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Travel must have
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the DIMJ Packing Cubes for Travel, and they exceeded my expectations. These lightweight and foldable organizer bags are a travel must-have. The beige color is stylish, and the cubes help keep my suitcase neatly organized. The quality is impressive, and they make packing and unpacking a breeze. Highly recommend for anyone looking to streamline their travel experience!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These help keep me organized they are definitely worth it. I give them 4 stars because the straps on the inside seem a little flimsy and I'm not quite sure what to do with the smaller ones since none of them are waterproof. I'm not sure how long they will last. Also the zippers are just normal pull zippers, not the circular ones shown in the pictures.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality for traveling
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for a vacation trip and it was great to have to keep organize. Good quality and good sizes for specific items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great variety of sizes
reviews.reviewText: These cubes are sooo useful. The variety of sizes and the sho bags came in very handy and made packing super easy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars The Quality Just Wasn’t There For Me
reviews.reviewText: For a low-priced organizer, I’m sure to most it’s fine. But to me they felt cheap, flimsy, with exposed stitching. I ended up sending them all back and buying more expensive ones from another travel brand. I felt it better to invest once in high-quality organizers that will last rather than have multiple sets of a so-so option.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Made packing easy
reviews.reviewText: The separate bags/pouches made it very easy for me to pack and compartmentalize my luggage. I was able to pack the small luggage me in my bag pack.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My sister introduced me to packing cubes so I wanted to find some that had a good variety of sizes so I can use to pack my clothes and my kids clothes when we travel. These are handy and offer a good variety of sizes. The zippers are smooth. one side is transparent so I can easily see what’s inside. Easy to clean.
